e Caesars (TV series)|The Caesars]]'', ''[[Freewheelers]]'').<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/obituaries/eric-flynn-9242936.html|last=Strachan|first=Alan|title=Eric Flynn|work=[[The Independent]], London|date=2002-03-14|accessdate=2019-04-18}}</ref>\n*[[Bernard Matemera]], 56, Zimbabwean sculptor.\n*[[Ernest Mercier (agronomist)|Ernest Mercier]], 88, Canadian  agronomist and deputy minister.\n*[[Elyne Mitchell]], 88,  Australian author\n*[[Prunella Ransome]], 59, English actress.\n*[[Velibor Vasovi\u0107]], 62, Serbian footballer and manager, heart attack.\n*[[Thomas Michael Whalen III]], 68, American attorney and politician (three-term mayor of [[Albany, New York|Albany]]), car accident.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/03/08/nyregion/thomas-m-whalen-iii-68-three-term-mayor-of-albany.html|last=Pace|first=Eric|title=Thomas M. Whalen III, 68, Three-Term Mayor of Albany|work=[[The New York Times]]|date=2002-03-08|accessdate=2019-05-01}}</ref>\n\n===5===\n*[[Howard Cannon]], 90, American politician ([[List of United States Senators from Nevada|U.S. Senator from Nevada]] from 1959 to 1983).<ref>{{cite news|url=http://bioguide.congress.gov/scripts/biodisplay.pl?index=C000120|title=CANNON, Howard Walter, (1912 - 2002)|work=[[Biographical Directory of the United States Congress]]|accessdate=2019-02-26}}</ref>\n*[[P\u00e9ter Kiss (mathematician)|P\u00e9ter Kiss]], 65, Hungarian mathematician.\n*[[Frances Macdonald (English artist)|Frances Macdonald]], 87, English painter.\n*[[William Nagle (author)|William Nagle]], 54, Australian soldier, author, actor, and screenwriter.\n*[[Huang Shun-hsing]], 78, Taiwanese politician, heart attack.\n*[[Clay Smith (baseball)|Clay Smith]], 87, American baseball player ([[Cleveland Indians]], [[Detroit Tigers]]).<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/smithcl01.shtml|title=Clay Smith|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com]]|accessdate=2019-02-20}}</ref>\n*[[Surendra Jha 'Suman']], 91, I